2001-02-12  perdig  <perdig@users.sourceforge.net>

	* /cvsroot/ggz/ggz/game_clients/chess/board.c, /cvsroot/ggz/ggz/game_clients/chess/board.h, /cvsroot/ggz/ggz/game_clients/chess/callbacks.c, /cvsroot/ggz/ggz/game_clients/chess/chess.h, /cvsroot/ggz/ggz/game_clients/chess/game.c, /cvsroot/ggz/ggz/game_clients/chess/net.c:
