2000-12-04  perdig  <perdig@users.sourceforge.net>

	* /cvsroot/ggz/ggz/game_clients/reversi/confio.c, /cvsroot/ggz/ggz/game_clients/reversi/confio.h, /cvsroot/ggz/ggz/game_clients/reversi/main_win.c:
